{"tid":1533410,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"社評：ZARA香港門店週一停業，什麼意思？","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:34:36.000Z","uid":53062,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b90176baff29de715d6355583646c8cadc0ba32","tid":1533410,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"下一個清算對象，ZARA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnKmBLN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F9CaKrnKmBLN&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=afb43804\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnKmBLN</a><br />\n節錄：<br />\nZara成為全球品牌，世界各地的穩定與繁榮支持了它的發展，它這些年從香港及中國內地市場收穫頗豐，同樣享受了這個國家和平進步的紅利。 目前香港出現動盪，威脅到廣大香港市民的根本利益，也給中國內地社會造成困擾，Zara善意回應香港止暴制亂的努力是其應有的一份表現，它不應在這方面發出令人 懷疑的信號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nZara需要做出鄭重說明並且糾正自己的做法，給香港愛國愛港的市民和內地廣大公眾一個嚴肅的交代。 如今香港的事情聚集了中國全社會的大量注意力，公眾不會接受Zara門店在香港的表現。  Zara不應做出嚴重的誤判。"},{"pid":"fc8cee779873bb5908e86bf7661f646efc523973","tid":1533410,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔